OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FKey areas of cancer data mandatorily
OL,8,Fpublished in the UK to manage wait
OL,9,Ftimes and treatment are not being
OL,10,Fpublished in the Channel Islands.
OL,12,FIt comes after a Freedom of
OL,13,FInformation request in Guernsey
OL,14,Fseeking information about staging
OL,15,Fdata, referral to treatment times, and
OL,16,Fthe accuracy of GP referrals was
OL,17,Frejected, as it would "require
OL,18,Fdisproportionate effort to compile".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FThe most recent publication on cancer
OL,8,Ftrends relies on figures from four
OL,9,Fyears ago, and one charity in Guernsey
OL,10,Fsays recent data is key to managing
OL,11,Ftheir work and helping patients.
OL,13,FWhat is published in the UK, unlike
OL,14,Fthe Channel Islands?
OL,16,FIn the UK, staging data - the number
OL,17,Fof people with cancer through stages
OL,18,Fone to four - is published monthly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FWhilst in Jersey and Guernsey, staging
OL,8,Ftrends and percentages are recorded in
OL,9,Fthe islands but not publicised.
OL,11,FThe UK also publishes the waiting time
OL,12,Fbetween GP referral and treatment,
OL,13,Falong with the conversion rate, which
OL,14,Fexplains how often a GP referral leads
OL,15,Fto a diagnosis.
OL,17,FHowever, this is not the case in the
OL,18,FChannel Islands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FDr Pat Price, an oncologist from the
OL,8,FImperial College of London, says
OL,9,Ffigures are relied on in the UK.
OL,11,F"What you really need is real-time
OL,12,Fdata now," she explains. "In the UK,
OL,13,Fperformance data is published each
OL,14,Fmonth, and while it's usually two
OL,15,Fmonths behind, it's really that up to
OL,16,Fdate.
OL,18,F"It's really important to have that,
OL,19,Fand you can go online and find that
OL,20,Fout."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FThe NHS use the data to help keep
OL,8,Fwaiting times down, reach people at
OL,9,Fstage one or two early, and the
OL,10,Fconversion rate helps monitor how well
OL,11,Fpathways to treatment are working.
OL,13,FDespite the Channel Island cancer
OL,14,Freport being published last year,
OL,15,Fcharities say up-to-date and detailed
OL,16,Fdata is essential.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FNaomi Leach, the Chair of Guernsey
OL,8,Fbreast cancer charity, Pink Ladies,
OL,9,Fexplains: "Most of our statistics are
OL,10,Fanecdotal; most of it is us talking to
OL,11,Fpeople in the community, or talking to
OL,12,Fpeople up at the hospital, so we don't
OL,13,Fhave a lot of information.
OL,15,F"The Channel Islands cancer report
OL,16,Fthat came out in December 2025 is up
OL,17,Fto '22 data."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FA statement from Jersey Health and
OL,8,FSocial Care specifically on staging
OL,9,Fdata says: "This information is held
OL,10,Fwithin the Somerset Cancer Register, a
OL,11,Fdigital registry that facilitates
OL,12,Fbetter coordination of care by
OL,13,Fallowing all involved specialists to
OL,14,Faccess up-to-date patient records.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,F"At present, publication of cancer
OL,8,Fstaging data would require manual
OL,9,Fextraction. The upcoming upgrade to
OL,10,Fthe Somerset Cancer Register will
OL,11,Fallow us to instantly report on cancer
OL,12,Fstaging in the coming months and help
OL,13,Fensure we're aligned with cancer
OL,14,Ftracking processes and care with UK
OL,15,Fbest practice."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FWhen asked for specific data in the
OL,8,FFOI request, Health and Social Care
OL,9,F(HSC) in Guernsey adds: "This request
OL,10,Fis highly specific and covers a
OL,11,Fsubstantial amount of detailed
OL,12,Finformation relating to cancer.
OL,14,F"While some data could theoretically
OL,15,Fbe derived from individual records, it
OL,16,Fis not held in an aggregated format.
OL,18,F"Producing it would require
OL,19,Fsignificant manual extraction and
OL,20,Fanalysis, representing an unreasonable
OL,21,Fdiversion of resources.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,F"In accordance with Section 2.9 of the
OL,8,FFreedom of Information Code, the
OL,9,FCommittee has determined that it will
OL,10,Fnot provide data that would require
OL,11,Fdisproportionate effort to compile."
OL,13,FBoth islands are finishing the
OL,14,Fintroduction of new electronic patient
OL,15,Frecord systems, which should be fully
OL,16,Fimplemented this year.
OL,18,FThis could see the data above
OL,19,Favailable for publication in the
OL,20,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1776280294
OL,3,CCancer referral and treatment data
OL,4,Ccannot yet be published in Channel
OL,5,CIslands
OL,7,FGuernsey's HSC says: "Following the
OL,8,Fimplementation of the new Electronic
OL,9,FPatient Record, it is intended that a
OL,10,Freferral-to-treatment measure will be
OL,11,Fintroduced in due course."
OL,13,FThe HCS in Jersey adds: "As digital
OL,14,Fsystems across Jersey's health system
OL,15,Fdevelop over time, we expect to
OL,16,Fimprove how we report endtoend
OL,17,Fwaiting times."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
